## Summary

This documentation covers the Android-Kotlin SDK for Amplitude analytics, including installation via Gradle/Maven (com.amplitude:analytics-android), configuration options like flushIntervalMillis/flushQueueSize, autocapture features (sessions, app lifecycles, screen views, deep links, element interactions), tracking methods (track, identify, revenue), user/device ID management, plugins system, and advanced features like offline mode and network tracking plugin.

